{"article_id":"9sCnXSBxK64LjWdB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Vice President Joe Biden , in an online video Thursday , officially declared his candidacy for president in 2020 ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"capping off weeks of intrigue and media speculation .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"He enters a crowded field of Democratic contenders","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"aiming to unseat President Trump","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"--","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"nearly 32 years after he announced his first campaign for president .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"The campaign is Biden ' s third for the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"having also unsuccessfully run in 1988 and 2008 .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` The core values of this nation , our standing in the world , our very democracy , everything","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that has made America","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"-- America --","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"is at stake .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"That ' s why today I ' m announcing my candidacy for president of the United States , ''","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Biden tweeted early Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"With the announcement ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"which followed months of deliberations ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Biden becomes a front-runner in an incredibly crowded field of Democratic presidential contenders all","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"vying to face off next year against Trump .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The president welcomed Biden into the race ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"warning him","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that the race will be `` nasty . ''","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` Welcome to the race Sleepy Joe , ''","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` I only hope","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"you have the intelligence , long in doubt ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to wage a successful primary campaign .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"It will be nasty -","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"you will be dealing with people","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"who truly have some very sick & demented ideas .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"if you make it ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"I will see you at the Starting Gate ! ''","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Biden , along with independent Sen. Bernie Sanders of Vermont","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"-- who is making his second straight White House run --","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"have consistently topped the polls in the race for the Democratic nomination .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"In Thursday 's video , the former vice president pointed to the violent clashes in Charlottesville , Virginia in August of 2017 at a large white nationalist rally ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Biden took aim at Trump ' s response","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"that \" there were some very fine people on both sides . \"","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"\" With those words , the president of the United assigned a moral equivalence between those","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"spreading hate","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"and those","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"with the courage","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"to stand against it , ''","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"Biden charged .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"`` And in that moment , I new","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"the threat to this nation was unlike any","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"I had seen in my lifetime .","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"I wrote at the time","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"that we ' re in the battle for the soul of this nation .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"Well , that ' s even more true today .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"We are in the battle for the soul of this nation . ''","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Biden argued","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"`` if we give Donald Trump eight years in the White House ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"he will forever and fundamentally alter the character of this nation ,","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"who we are ,","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"and I can not stand by","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"and watch that happen . ''","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"reported last week","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that the theme of the announcement would be ' the battle for the soul of America . '","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Biden is expected to follow up the announcement with his first high-dollar fundraiser in the Philadelphia home of Comcast executive David Cohen Thursday evening","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"and appear at a local union hall in Pittsburgh on Monday .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"The former Delaware senator has for weeks been rallying potential donors in an effort","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to gain momentum ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that Sanders and former Rep. Beto O'Rourke of Texas managed to raise $ 6 million within 24 hours","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"of launching their candidacy .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"The Biden campaign said","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"that the former vice president will lay out his \" vision","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"for rebuilding America ' s middle class \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"at the Pittsburgh event .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Then he ' s scheduled to travel to the four states","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that vote first in the primary and caucus nominating calendar .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"They add","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that Biden will hold a rally in Philadelphia on May 18 , likely at the city ' s Museum of Art","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"- known nationally for the scene of the fictional Rocky Balboa ' s training on the museum ' s steps in the movie `` Rocky . \"","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"The start and finish of his initial campaign swing in Pennsylvania is no surprise .","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"The state","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"- long a crucial battleground in presidential elections -","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"was one of the key states","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Trump flipped in the 2016 election","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"to help him capture the White House .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"And","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"while Biden has long lived in Delaware","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"and represented that state for nearly four decades in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"he was born","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"and spent his early years in Scranton , Pennsylvania","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"and the Keystone State has always remained special to him .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Moments after his announcement , Biden was endorsed by Sen. Bob Casey of Pennsylvania .","depth":3},{"id":89,"text":"Biden ' s long awaited and much anticipated presidential campaign launch comes","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"after facing allegations in recent weeks from women","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"that he had made them feel uncomfortable in the past with what was described as inappropriate touching .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"It instantly become a top story online and on the cable news networks ,","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"forcing the former vice president to play defense in the # MeToo era and defend his decades old brand of close up and personal politics","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"`` Social norms are changing .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"I understand that ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"and I 've heard what these women are saying , ''","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Biden explained in a video","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"released during the height of the furor ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"which threatened his looming candidacy .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"`` Politics to me has always been about making connections ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"but I will be more mindful about respecting personal space in the future .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"That 's my responsibility","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"and I will meet it . ''","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"While Biden didn ' t apologize to those","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"who raised the allegations ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he did say","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"`` I ' m sorry","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"I didn ' t understand more .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"I ' m not sorry for any of my intentions .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"I ' m not sorry for anything","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"I ' ve ever done .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"I ' ve never been disrespectful intentionally to a man or a woman . \"","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"referring to well-publicized past episodes","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"of getting too close for comfort with fellow politicians , their family members and others ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"the former vice president explained","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that `` it is incumbent on me and everybody else to make sure","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"if you embrace someone ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"if you touch someone ,","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"it ' s with their consent ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"regardless of your intentions . ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"While the controversy was dominating headlines ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Biden ' s inner circle was continuing to reach out to Democratic operatives","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"as they quietly mapped out a national campaign structure as well as staff in the early voting primary and caucus states .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"And in the days","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"leading up to the launch ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"Biden picked up the pace","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"on reaching out to top donors and supporters ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"with the acknowledgment","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"that he ' ll be judged by how much he fundraising dollars","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"he hauls in in the first 24 hours","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"after declaring his candidacy .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Biden has long had his eyes on his presidency :","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"In June of 1987 , Biden first launched a bid for the 1988 Democratic nomination.","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"The then-senator from Delaware was considered one of the stronger candidates in the emerging Democratic field .","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"But three months into his campaign , he faced newspaper headlines","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"that he had plagiarized a speech by British politician Neil Kinnock .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"The incident sparked a controversy ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"knocking Biden out of the race well before the start of the primaries and caucuses .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Biden ran a second time for the Democratic nomination in the 2008 cycle ,","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"declaring his candidacy in January of 2007 .","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"Despite his long record ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"his campaign never caught lightning in a bottle .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"There were also some well-publicized gaffes ,","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"including his description of then-Sen. Barack Obama .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"`` I mean ,","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"you got the first mainstream African-American","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"who is articulate and bright and clean and a nice-looking guy , ''","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"Biden said at the time .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"`` I mean ,","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"that 's a storybook , man. \"","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"The comments quickly spelled trouble for Biden ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"forcing him to apologize .","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"Biden ' s bid was also overshadowed by Obama and then-Sen. Hillary Clinton of New York ,","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"who ended up battling each other in an historic and marathon quest for the nomination .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"Biden dropped out of the race","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"after coming in fifth in the Iowa caucus ,","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"grabbing less than one percent of the vote .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"But seven months later , Obama selected Biden as his running mate .","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"The pair won the November 2008 election ,","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"and were re-elected in 2012 .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"Biden seriously considered another run for the White House in 2016 ,","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"but","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"grappling with the death of his eldest son Beau ,","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"the Vice President announced in October of 2015","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"that he would not launch a campaign .","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Speaking from the podium at the Rose Garden ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Biden explained","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"that he had been emotionally drained by the death of his son","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"and stressed","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"that `` nobody has a right ...","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"to seek that office","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"unless they 're willing to give it 110 percent of who they are . \"","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"But the decision","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"not to run","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"haunted him .","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"He noted in early 2016","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"that he regretted not running \" every day . \"","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"Trump ' s upset victory over Clinton in the 2016 presidential election changed the dynamic for Biden .","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"He soon became a vocal critic of the Republican in the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"and speculation sprang up","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"that Biden would consider a final presidential bid in 2020 .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"Trips to New Hampshire in 2017 and to Iowa , South Carolina and Iowa in 2018 fueled the flames .","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"Biden dropped a major hint of his pending 2020 campaign in early March .","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"After walking to the podium at the at the annual convention of the International Association of Fire Fighters","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"( IAFF )","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"to chants of \" run Joe , run , \" by the union crowd ,","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"Biden said","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"\" I appreciate the energy","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"you showed","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"when I got up here .","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"Save it a little longer .","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"I may need it in a few weeks . \"","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"The comments brought a standing ovation from the mostly blue collar audience","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"that Biden feels","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"he can count on","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"as he runs for president .","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"In early April , Biden told reporters","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"`` I am very close to making a decision","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"to stand before you all relatively soon . ''","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"Asked why the hold-up ,","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"Biden quickly answered ,","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"`` The hold-up is to put everything together . ''","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"At the time , Biden also pushed back against the perception","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"that he 's a moderate in a party","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"that 's increasingly moving to the left .","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"He defended himself ,","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"he 'll stack his record against `` anybody","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"who has run","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"or who is running now","depth":15},{"id":214,"text":"or who will run . ''","depth":15},{"id":215,"text":"And","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"highlighting his early public push for same-sex marriage during the Obama administration ,","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"he stressed","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"`` I 'm not sure","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"when everybody else came out","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"and said","depth":15},{"id":221,"text":"they 're for gay marriage . ''","depth":15},{"id":222,"text":"Biden was born on November 20 , 1942 ,","depth":6},{"id":223,"text":"and lived in Scranton , Pennsylvania for ten years","depth":7},{"id":224,"text":"until moving with his family to Delaware .","depth":7},{"id":225,"text":"He became an attorney in 1969","depth":7},{"id":226,"text":"and was elected to the New Castle City Council in 1970 .","depth":7},{"id":227,"text":"He won what was out the outset a long-shot election to the Senate two years later ,","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"becoming the sixth-youngest senator in the nation ' s history .","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"He was re-elected six times","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"before resigning in 2009","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"to take on the duties as vice president .","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"During his nearly four decades in the Senate , he was a longtime member and former chair of the Foreign Relations Committee .","depth":9},{"id":233,"text":"He also served as chairman of the Senate Judiciary Committee .","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"But Biden ' s role as Judiciary Committee chairman in 1991 during the confirmation hearings of Supreme Court nominee Clarence Thomas is arguably more controversial today","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"than it was at the time nearly three decades ago .","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"In March he lamented the impact of `` white man 's culture ''","depth":15},{"id":237,"text":"and bemoaned his own role in the hearings","depth":16},{"id":238,"text":"that undermined witness Anita Hill 's credibility .","depth":16},{"id":239,"text":"Biden said","depth":15},{"id":240,"text":"that Hill ,","depth":17},{"id":241,"text":"who is black ,","depth":17},{"id":242,"text":"should not have been forced to face a panel of `` a bunch of white guys '' about her sexual harassment allegations against Thomas ,","depth":17},{"id":243,"text":"who was nominated by President George H.W . Bush .","depth":17},{"id":244,"text":"`` To this day I regret","depth":16},{"id":245,"text":"I could n't come up with a way","depth":17},{"id":246,"text":"to give her the kind of hearing","depth":18},{"id":247,"text":"she deserved , ''","depth":18},{"id":248,"text":"he said .","depth":15},{"id":249,"text":"`` I wish","depth":15},{"id":250,"text":"I could have done something . ''","depth":15},{"id":251,"text":"But his comments elicited derision by many women ,","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"who argued","depth":14},{"id":253,"text":"that as the chairman of the committee , he had the power","depth":15},{"id":254,"text":"to do something .","depth":15},{"id":255,"text":"Biden married his wife Neilia in 1966 .","depth":5},{"id":256,"text":"In 1972 , soon after his election to the Senate , his wife and their daughter Naomi were killed in an automobile accident .","depth":7},{"id":257,"text":"Sons Beau and Hunter Biden survived .","depth":7},{"id":258,"text":"He married his second and current wife Jill five years later .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":517,"left":347,"right":516,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":347,"left":334,"right":346,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":334,"left":276,"right":333,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":266,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":264,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":260,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":262,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent"